welcomeText:
# Heights Stake Trek 2023 "Be Still and Know That I Am God"

Trek begins Wed, July 26th 7am. Parents, use the southwest entrance to drop off all youth trekkers and gear (select Information above for all info) by the pavilion at the 16/18/24/DryCreek ward building (720 E 550 N) Do not forget your sack lunch! Do not pack anything that is not on the list. If you do, no worries, we will hold onto it for you until trek is over. Trek ends Sat, July 29th 3pm. Parents, pick up all youth trekkers at the same location where they were dropped off: the 16/18/24/DryCreek ward building (720 E 550 N) **Mosquito Alert!** There have been reports of plenty of mosquitos up at the Trek site, each trekker should bring insect repellent AND a mosquito head net is highly recommended. You will be so glad you did! **Dont forget SUNGLASSES!** The sun shines brightly on the Wyoming plains, and we forgot to put sunglasses on your packing list, please remember sunglasses. 2023 Heights Trek photos and videos now available. Touch or click Invormation above and then Trek Videos.
